commit.message:
Add minimal test for DeviceAppender.

Fix omission: DeviceAppender does not call destructorImpl().
Modernize.
Add concept requirements to variadic Socket::write().

Two more tweaks.

Constexpr and missing concept.
Remove debug output from test.
Use std::this_thread::yield().
Use C++ concepts a little.
Fix warnings.
Mark tstring_hash operators noexcept.
Test update with Automake 1.16j.

Use string_view in MDC API.

Fix use of moved-from object.
mdc.cxx: Clear MDC before tests.
Fix leaks and use after free in tests in objectregistry.cxx.

Check for C++23 compat, not C++20 compat.

We are using C++20 on this branch.

Update with Autoconf 2.72.

Invoke AC_SYS_YEAR2038 macro.

MDC: Implement MDCGuard.

This bring MDC API changes.
Two Doxygen docs fixes.
Use __format__ in attribute.
Check for init_priority attribute in CMake based build.

Turn off Mac OS X GitHub action build.

Mac OS X is missing std::format in <format> header.
Use GCC 10 in GitHub actions.
Add logging macros LOG4CPLUS_*_FORMAT() based on C++20 std::format.
Use override keyword in more places.
Use std::filesystem::path when opening fstream.
Check for __attribute__((__constructor__(prio))) with CMake, too.
Fix preprocess condition enabling __builtin_FILE(), etc.
Remove LOG4CPLUS_LIKELY and LOG4CPLUS_UNLIKELY.
